{"tid":2153180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Tesla在中國成立保險公司","createTime":"2020-08-12T11:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T11:54:00.000Z","uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"73a90dddc93b96e4c1065c4ef42e8f27c0bee882","tid":2153180,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:24:38.000Z","msg":"電動車廠特斯拉（Tesla）執行長馬斯克（Elon Musk）一直想拓展汽車保險業務，雖曾被「股神」巴菲特（Warren Buffett）酸成功率恐怕跟「保險公司製造汽車」一樣，不過馬斯克沒有放棄，仍在6日於中國成立「特斯拉保險經紀有限公司」。<br />\n<br />\n《澎湃新聞》今天報導，中國網站「天眼查」的訊息顯示，特斯拉已於本月6日註冊「特斯拉保險經紀有限公司」，登記地點與上海特斯拉超級工廠相同，資本額為5000萬人民幣，業務範圍為「保險經紀」，由「特斯拉汽車香港有限公司」持有100%股份，並由特斯拉大中華區負責人朱曉彤擔任此公司的法定代表人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3258191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3258191&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7QZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=0f37b3ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3258191&h=95a9d856\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3258191</a>"},{"pid":"4de2454219a637f4a3e7af6c97d29fd7d90ff677","tid":2153180,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"是旦啦<br />\n佢要死唔通唔畀人死咩"},{"pid":"82957344c1d697a230d0b9cc015438eab3494ca2","tid":2153180,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"輸鳩死佢啦以支那人既性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f000cc259bd5ca2a75d5abba24419ed52b1ace","tid":2153180,"uid":68598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"係支那洗鬼買tesla咩 <br />\n買恆馳咪得 <br />\n有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f4b5fbde170dc301cf9d8b125b51da1b9e8107","tid":2153180,"uid":111153,"like":0,